  "title": "<div>theres no gap between </div>",
  "content": "<div>theres no gap between </div>\n<div>where you were last broken</div>\n<div>and where i fell in love</div>\n<div>theres no gap</div>\n<div>a ton of overlap</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>you cant play these games with me</div>\n<div>i wont play these goddamned games</div>\n<div>still i'll let you play me</div>\n<div>anyway anywhere anyhow</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>when youre alone you reach</div>\n<div>to me knowing im there waiting</div>\n<div>through the black glass</div>\n<div>touch my digital hand</div>\n<div>i wanna hold you with arms that can feel</div>\n<div>i wanna hold you</div>\n<div>cause you look so frail and so am i</div>\n<div>but i see how we fit</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>your cracked egg smiling face</div>\n<div>hides deep under covers </div>\n<div>of silk and lace</div>\n<div>so very very deep deep down</div>\n<div>your silhouette cant hide from me</div>\n<div>i can see through to you</div>\n<div>i can see through you</div>\n<div><img style=\"max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,",
